which features a comprehensive collection of well-designed, innovative, sophisticated, functional and fun products for babies, toddlers, kids and their families.</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial">We ask that you contact Sarah Collins &amp; Zoe Maliszewski (copied on this email) to inquire about securing placement as soon as possible.</font><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial">On behalf of the Handmade Selection Committee, we wish you continued success.</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial">Sincerely,</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial">Ashley Ciofrone| Sales Manager | 914-421-3310</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">Andrea Colagiovanni | Sales Representative | 914-421-3280</div>]]></td>
